snippet.title: Arthur Christmas
snippet.description: Santa and his elite elf team use spy-like stunts to deliver billions of presents to all the world's children in one incredible night. So what does it mean if only one child gets left without a present? Everything! Now it is up to Santa's youngest son Arthur to fix this slip up and make good on the promise of Christmas. With the help of retired Grand Santa and a rebellious young elf, Arthur's on a last-second ride to give the final gift and bring wonder back to the holiday season. snippet.title: Where The Heart Is
snippet.description: Novalee Nation (Natalie Portman), 17 and very pregnant, has never been part of a real home.  The closest thing to family for the hard-luck teen is her selfish, would-be musician boyfriend, Willy Jack, with whom she's traveling from Tennessee to California in a rust bucket that used to be a Plymouth.  A bathroom stop en route, at an Oklahoma Wal-Mart, changes Novalee's life forever.  For when she leaves the store, she discovers that Willy Jack and the Plymouth are gone. Forced to take refuge back in the store, Novalee has her baby in the aisles of Wal-Mart and becomes an overnight celebrity. At long last, Novalee begins to put her life together with the help of the quirky strangers who become her surrogate family.

snippet.title: Club Penguin - An MMORPG Story
snippet.description:
Documentary about Club Penguin, for it's 15th anniversary.

Featuring:
Chris Hendricks
Lance Priebe
Lane Merrifield

Club Penguin was an online-based, massively multiplayer online role-playing game (abbreviated as a MMORPG) created by Disney Canada Inc. (previously New Horizons Interactive) in the summer of 2005. The game was founded by Lance Priebe, and co-founded by Lane Merrifield, and Dave Krysko. There were over 330,000,000 penguin accounts created and played in over 190 countries. It was estimated that over 150 million people worldwide play Club Penguin. It was discontinued on March 30, 2017.

More from the creators + Further reading:

About WOA Luka Channel:
The channel mainly focuses on a clay character named Luka and his family including mother and his little sister. Together, they go through struggle everyday to learn many lessons about good behaviors.
All of our contents is designed with the purpose of children's education based on their ages and development.
For a better future, we hope kids and parents will recognize good behaviors and essential life skills through our videos:
❤️ Problem solving in tough situations.
🧡 Interpersonal relationship with parents and family.
💛 Empathy with animals other non-human beings.
💚 Positive thinking and coping with stress
💙 Coping with emotion, learning unification and make friends
According to their ages, we build some topics that can be related to real life education:
❤️ Discovery: developing imagination with costumes, exploring environment
🧡 Initial lessons: learning letters, colors, numbers, housework
💛 Protecting surrounding environment
💚 Profession training: doctor, teacher, police, firefighter,...
Not just only for children’s self education, parents can also learn the good way to teach their children. To a brighter generation, we hope our content can convey useful message to the community.

About WOA Luka Channel:
The channel mainly focuses on a clay character named Luka and his family including mother and his little sister. Together, they go through struggle everyday to learn many lessons about good behaviors.
All of our contents is designed with the purpose of children's education based on their ages and development.
For a better future, we hope kids and parents will recognize good behaviors and essential life skills through our videos:
❤️ Problem solving in tough situations.
🧡 Interpersonal relationship with parents and family.
💛 Empathy with animals other non-human beings.
💚 Positive thinking and coping with stress
💙 Coping with emotion, learning unification and make friends
According to their ages, we build some topics that can be related to real life education:
❤️ Discovery: developing imagination with costumes, exploring environment
🧡 Initial lessons: learning letters, colors, numbers, housework
💛 Protecting surrounding environment
💚 Profession training: doctor, teacher, police, firefighter,...
Not just only for children’s self education, parents can also learn the good way to teach their children. To a brighter generation, we hope our content can convey useful message to the community.
We release a new episode everyday. Stay tuned and hit the subscribe button and ring bell for not missing any.
